<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als <expan>vorczeite<ex>n</ex></expan>
                            der hochgeporn fürst und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Margraf Jobs von
                            Merhern <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>kaufleute<ex>n</ex></expan>
                            ir habe und <expan>kauffma<ex>n</ex>s<ex>chaft</ex></expan> czu Prunne
                                    <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, hat uns der
                                    <expan>hochg<ex>eporn</ex></expan> fürst und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> burgraf
                                <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> nü newlich
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, wie er mit
                                    <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>Margr<ex>af</ex></expan> Jobsen von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> davon geredt habt; darauff im <add>gar
                                glimpflich</add>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hab und als auch
                                    <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rysbeck, <expan>weis<ex>er</ex></expan>
                            dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>, darümb czu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add>weish<ex>eit</ex></add> kümt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
                            ir im durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> gen <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Margr<ex>af</ex></expan> Jobsen <add>darynne</add>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige <expan>fürdr<ex>ung</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                                    <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</del><app>
<note place="inline">Abest</note>
</app></ab>
</div>
